{"tid":1148023,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇亞雷斯膝蓋受傷 恐缺席今夏美洲盃","createTime":"2019-05-10T07:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T11:20:07.000Z","uid":173952,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"420f3ce6cdf3413df0b8ea71914ce340b76a4f94","tid":1148023,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T07:59:19.000Z","msg":"據巴塞官方的消息，蘇亞雷斯（L.Suarez）將因為膝蓋傷勢缺席今季的賸餘比賽。<br />\n<br />\n  除了缺席剩餘的兩場西甲比賽，他也將缺席與華倫西亞的西班牙盃決賽，甚至有可能缺席今夏進行的美洲盃比賽。<br />\n<br />\n  週四，蘇亞雷斯進行了關節鏡檢查，他將進行膝蓋方面的治療。蘇亞雷斯飽受膝蓋傷病的困擾，他現在選擇進行手術，也是為了能夠在下季迎來最好的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n蘇亞雷斯可能缺席美洲盃<br />\n<br />\n  今季蘇亞雷斯為巴塞攻入25球，是巴塞贏西甲冠軍的功臣之一，也是巴塞晉級西班牙盃決賽的關鍵球員"},{"pid":"cdb30b6fefca29b6c1b8b6ef94b45081445e75f0","tid":1148023,"uid":103207,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"帶傷上陣報恩,錯怪SO9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfde877864a448e288d07a1bcfa161df915057d5","tid":1148023,"uid":33436,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"陰濕野做得多有報應？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840e9db7d9a3ce2c93a782056058952d539eb1b2","tid":1148023,"uid":53855,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:03:40.000Z","msg":"唔敢贏美斯&hellip;"},{"pid":"ebb95d7ec90e48159adc1c8d7a24cf6653de822e","tid":1148023,"uid":173952,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"840e9db7d9a3ce2c93a782056058952d539eb1b2","tid":1148023,"uid":53855,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:03:40.000Z","msg":"唔敢贏美斯&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nUoJajy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnUoJajy.jpg&h=2c0bb6ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿蘇拎過啦，今年豪比你"},{"pid":"594922d4b2b5fbdb9a13ea2573afd77ac027917e","tid":1148023,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebb95d7ec90e4